  <para style="h">Abaefeso</para>
  <para style="toc1">Ebbaluwa ya Pawulo Omutukuvu eri Abaefeso</para>
  <para style="toc2">Abaefeso</para>
  <para style="toc3">Bef</para>
  <para style="mt2">Ebbaluwa ya Pawulo Omutukuvu eri</para>
  <para style="mt1">Abaefeso</para>
  <para style="imt">Ennyanjula</para>
  <para style="ip">Pawulo Omutukuvu yawandiika ebbaluwa eno nga musibe e Ruumi wakati w’emyaka <char style="sc">ad</char> 58 ne 64. Kye yagenderera kwe kugumya n’okuzzaamu amaanyi abakkiriza abaali mu Asiya Entono (kaakano eyitibwa Butuluuki). Pawulo abayisaayisa mu byafaayo, ng’atandikira ku nteekateeka za Katonda ezikwata ku nsi yonna, n’atuuka ne mu biseera bya leero Katonda mw’alokolera abakkiriza Kristo, bw’atyo n’ayigiriza ne ku biseera eby’omu maaso, ebigenda okujja, ng’olwo omulabe Setaani awanguddwa. Annyonnyola nti mu biseera bino wajja kubaawo okulwanagana okw’amaanyi ne Setaani (<char style="xt"><ref loc="EPH 6:12">6:12</ref></char>). Kyokka olwokubanga tuli mubiri gwa Kristo, atuwa amaanyi agatumala okweteekerateekera omulabe oyo. Pawulo n’alyoka ayigiriza ku ebyo ebikwata ku mbeera y’Omukristaayo n’engeri gy’asaana okweyisaamu buli lunaku. N’akoona ku bufumbo, n’empisa ennungi. Abuulirira abazadde, n’abaana abato era n’abaddu ng’abategeeza engeri Omukristaayo gy’asaana okutambulamu mu kkubo lino ery’Obukristaayo.</para>
  <para style="ie"/>
  <chapter number="1" style="c"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:1 a </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1CO 1:1">1Ko 1:1</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">b </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="2CO 1:1">2Ko 1:1</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">c </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="COL 1:2">Bak 1:2</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nze Pawulo, omutume wa Kristo Yesu, olw’okwagala kwa Katonda, mpandiikira abatukuvu abali mu Efeso, era abakkiririza mu Kristo Yesu.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:2 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 1:7">Bar 1:7</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Ekisa n’emirembe ebiva eri Katonda Kitaffe ne Mukama waffe Yesu Kristo bibeerenga nammwe.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="s1">Emikisa mu Kristo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:3 a </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="2CO 1:3">2Ko 1:3</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">b </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EPH 2:6">Bef 2:6</ref>; <ref loc="EPH 3:10">3:10</ref>; <ref loc="EPH 6:12">6:12</ref></char>
    </note>Yeebazibwe Katonda era Kitaawe wa Mukama waffe Yesu Kristo, atuwadde mu Kristo buli mukisa gwonna ogw’omwoyo oguva mu ggulu. <verse number="4" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:4 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EPH 5:27">Bef 5:27</ref>; <ref loc="COL 1:22">Bak 1:22</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EPH 4:2">Bef 4:2</ref>, <ref loc="EPH 4:15">15</ref>, <ref loc="EPH 4:16">16</ref></char></note>Yatulonda okubeera mu Kristo ng’ensi tennatondebwa, ffe tube batukuvu, abataliiko kya kunenyezebwa mu maaso ge, olw’okwagala kwe. <verse number="5" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:5 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 8:29">Bar 8:29</ref>, <ref loc="ROM 8:30">30</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 1:21">1Ko 1:21</ref></char></note>Olw’okwagala kwe, yatuteekateeka tubeere abaana be mu Yesu Kristo, ng’okusiima kwe bwe kuli. <verse number="6" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:6 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 3:17">Mat 3:17</ref></char></note>Katonda tumutendereze olw’ekisa kye yatuwa obuwa mu Mwana, gw’ayagala ennyo. <verse number="7" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:7 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 3:24">Bar 3:24</ref></char></note>Mu oyo mwe tununulibwa olw’omusaayi gwe, ne tusonyiyibwa ebibi, ng’obugagga bw’ekisa kye bwe buli, <verse number="8" style="v"/>kye yatuwa mu bungi mu magezi gonna ne mu kutegeera kwonna. <verse number="9" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:9 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 16:25">Bar 16:25</ref></char></note>Yatubikkulira ekyama eky’okwagala kwe, ng’okusiima kwe bwe kuli kwe yateekerateekera mu Kristo. <verse number="10" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:10 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GAL 4:4">Bag 4:4</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="COL 1:20">Bak 1:20</ref></char></note>Olwo ekiseera ekituufu bwe kirituuka, Katonda alikola byonna bye yateekateeka, n’ateeka ebintu byonna awamu wansi wa Kristo, ebiri mu ggulu n’ebiri ku nsi.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:11 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EPH 3:11">Bef 3:11</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Era mu ye mwe twaweerwa obusika ne twawulibwa ng’enteekateeka bw’eri ey’oyo akola ebintu byonna okusinziira ku magezi ag’okwagala kwe; <verse number="12" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:12 </char><char style="xt" closed="false">nny 6, 14</char></note>ffe Abayudaaya tulyoke tumuleetere okugulumizibwa, ffe abaasooka okuba n’essuubi mu Kristo. <verse number="13" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:13 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="COL 1:5">Bak 1:5</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EPH 4:30">Bef 4:30</ref></char></note>Nammwe, Kristo yabaleeta eri amazima, kye kigambo eky’Enjiri ey’okulokolebwa kwammwe. Bwe mwamukkiriza, ne muteekebwako envumbo eya Mwoyo Mutukuvu eyasuubizibwa, <verse number="14" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:14 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 20:32">Bik 20:32</ref></char></note>gwe musingo gw’obusika bwaffe, okutuusa bw’alinunula abantu be, ne Katonda n’agulumizibwa era n’atenderezebwa.</para>
  <para style="s1">Okusaba kwa Pawulo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:15 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="COL 1:4">Bak 1:4</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Noolwekyo okuva lwe nawulira okukkiriza kwe mulina mu Mukama waffe Yesu, n’okwagala kwe mulina eri abantu ba Katonda bonna, <verse number="16" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:16 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 1:8">Bar 1:8</ref></char></note>sirekangayo kwebaza Katonda ku lwammwe. Mbajjukira <verse number="17" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:17 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 20:17">Yk 20:17</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="COL 1:9">Bak 1:9</ref></char></note>ne mbasabira, Katonda wa Mukama waffe Yesu Kristo, Kitaffe ow’ekitiibwa, abawe Omwoyo ow’amagezi n’okubikkulirwa mweyongere okumutegeera. <verse number="18" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:18 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 26:18">Bik 26:18</ref>; <ref loc="2CO 4:6">2Ko 4:6</ref></char></note>Nnyongera okubasabira, amaaso g’emitima gyammwe gamulisibwenga, mulyoke mumanye essuubi ly’okuyitibwa kwammwe, n’obugagga obungi bwe mulina mu ye, mmwe awamu n’abantu ba Katonda bonna. <verse number="19" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:19 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="COL 1:29">Bak 1:29</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EPH 6:10">Bef 6:10</ref></char></note>Njagala mutegeere amaanyi ge agasukkiridde agakolera mu ffe abakkiriza, ng’okukola kw’obuyinza bw’amaanyi ge bwe kuli, <verse number="20" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:20 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 2:24">Bik 2:24</ref></char></note>amaanyi ago ge yakozesa mu Kristo bwe yamuzuukiza mu bafu, n’amutuuza ku mukono gwe ogwa ddyo waggulu mu ggulu. <verse number="21" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:21 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PHP 2:9">Baf 2:9</ref>, <ref loc="PHP 2:10">10</ref></char></note>Waggulu eyo, Kristo gy’afugira obufuzi bwonna, n’obuyinza bwonna, n’amaanyi gonna, n’obwami bwonna, na buli kitiibwa kyonna ekiweebwa omuntu. Afugira mu mulembe guno, era alifugira ne mu mulembe ogugenda okujja. <verse number="22" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:22 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 28:18">Mat 28:18</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EPH 4:15">Bef 4:15</ref>; <ref loc="EPH 5:23">5:23</ref></char></note>Katonda atadde ebintu byonna wansi w’ebigere bye, n’afuula Kristo omutwe gw’ebintu byonna eby’ekkanisa, <verse number="23" style="v"/>era ekkanisa gwe mubiri gwe ye yennyini, mwatuukiririza ebintu byonna.</para>
  <chapter number="2" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Okuggyibwa mu kufa n’okufuulibwa abalamu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">nny 5; <ref loc="COL 2:13">Bak 2:13</ref></char>
    </note>Edda mwali mufiiridde mu byonoono byammwe ne mu bibi byammwe. <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:2 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="COL 3:7">Bak 3:7</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 12:31">Yk 12:31</ref>; <ref loc="EPH 6:12">Bef 6:12</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">c </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EPH 5:6">Bef 5:6</ref></char></note>Ebyo bye mwatambulirangamu ng’emirembe egy’ensi bwe giri, nga mufugibwa omwoyo ogw’omukulu w’obuyinza obw’omu bbanga, omwoyo ogwa Setaani, ogufuga abajeemu bonna. <verse number="3" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:3 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GAL 5:16">Bag 5:16</ref></char></note>Edda naffe twatambuliranga mu kwegomba kw’emibiri gyaffe, nga tukola ebyo ebyegombebwanga omubiri n’ebirowoozo. Era okufaanana ng’abantu abalala bonna, naffe mu buzaaliranwa twali baakubonerezebwa ng’abalala bonna. <verse number="4" style="v"/>Kyokka olw’okwagala kwe okungi, n’ekisa kye ekingi, <verse number="5" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:5 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false">nny 1 </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false">nny 8; <ref loc="ACT 15:11">Bik 15:11</ref></char></note>ne bwe twali nga tufiiridde mu bibi byaffe, yatufuula abalamu awamu ne Kristo. Mwalokolebwa lwa kisa. <verse number="6" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:6 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EPH 1:20">Bef 1:20</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EPH 1:3">Bef 1:3</ref></char></note>Katonda yatuzuukiriza wamu ne Kristo okuva mu kufa ne tufuna obulamu, era atutuuzizza mu bifo eby’omu ggulu, okumpi ne Kristo Yesu. <verse number="7" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:7 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="TIT 3:4">Tit 3:4</ref></char></note>Ekyo Katonda yakikola alyoke alage, mu mirembe egigenda okujja, ekisa kye ekingi kye yatukwatirwa mu Kristo Yesu. <verse number="8" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:8 </char><char style="xt" closed="false">nny 5</char></note>Mwalokolebwa lwa kisa olw’okukkiriza. Tekwava mu mmwe, wabula kirabo kya Katonda. <verse number="9" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:9 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2TI 1:9">2Ti 1:9</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 1:29">1Ko 1:29</ref></char></note>Tekwatuweebwa lwa bikolwa byaffe; noolwekyo omuntu yenna aleme okwenyumirizanga. <verse number="10" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:10 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EPH 4:24">Bef 4:24</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="TIT 2:14">Tit 2:14</ref></char></note>Tuli mulimu gwa Katonda, abaatondebwa mu Kristo Yesu, okukolanga ebikolwa ebirungi, nga Katonda bwe yatuteekerateekera.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>Noolwekyo mujjukire, ng’edda mmwe abaali Abaamawanga mu mubiri, abaayitibwanga abatali bakomole abo abeeyita abaakomolebwa, kyokka nga baakomolebwa mu mubiri na ngalo z’abantu, <verse number="12" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:12 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GAL 3:17">Bag 3:17</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TH 4:13">1Bs 4:13</ref></char></note>nga mu biro biri temwamanya Kristo. Temwabalirwa mu ggwanga lya Isirayiri, era ng’Abaamawanga, temwalina mugabo mu ndagaano ya Katonda ey’ekisuubizo. Mwali wala ne Katonda, nga n’essuubi temulina. <verse number="13" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:13 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false">nny 17; <ref loc="ACT 2:39">Bik 2:39</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="COL 1:20">Bak 1:20</ref></char></note>Naye kaakano mu Kristo Yesu, mmwe abaali ewala mwasembezebwa olw’omusaayi gwa Kristo.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>Kristo gy’emirembe gyaffe, oyo eyatufuula ffe Abayudaaya nammwe Abaamawanga, okuba omuntu omu, ng’amenyeewo ekisenge ekya wakati eky’obulabe, ekyatwawulanga. <verse number="15" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:15 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="COL 1:21">Bak 1:21</ref>, <ref loc="COL 1:22">22</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="COL 2:14">Bak 2:14</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">c </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GAL 3:28">Bag 3:28</ref></char></note>Yadibya n’etteeka mu mateeka, alyoke yeetondemu omuntu omuggya ava mu babiri, ng’aleeta emirembe, <verse number="16" style="v"/>alyoke atabaganye ababiri okufuuka omubiri gumu eri Katonda olw’omusaalaba, bwe yazikiririza obulabe ku gwo. <verse number="17" style="v"/>Yajja okubuulira emirembe abo abaali ewala ne Katonda, n’abo abaali okumpi naye. <verse number="18" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:18 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EPH 3:12">Bef 3:12</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="COL 1:12">Bak 1:12</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">c </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 12:13">1Ko 12:13</ref></char></note>Ku bw’oyo Kristo ffenna tuyita mu Mwoyo omu okutuuka eri Kitaffe.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:19 a </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">nny 12 </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">b </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PHP 3:20">Baf 3:20</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">c </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GAL 6:10">Bag 6:10</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Noolwekyo temukyali baamawanga oba abagwira, wabula muli ba kika kimu n’abatukuvu, abantu ba Katonda, era muli ba mu nnyumba ya Katonda. <verse number="20" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:20 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1PE 2:4-8">1Pe 2:4-8</ref></char></note>Mwazimbibwa ku musingi ogw’abatume ne bannabbi, nga Kristo Yesu ly’ejjinja ekkulu ery’oku nsonda. <verse number="21" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:21 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 3:16">1Ko 3:16</ref>, <ref loc="1CO 3:17">17</ref></char></note>Mu oyo ffenna tuzimbibwa wamu ne tugattibwa wamu ne tubeera essinzizo ettukuvu mu Mukama waffe. <verse number="22" style="v"/>Era nammwe mwazimbibwa wamu mu kizimbe ekyo Kristo ky’azimbye okubeeranga ekifo Omwoyo wa Katonda mwabeera.</para>
  <chapter number="3" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Omulimu gwa Pawulo mu Baamawanga</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ACT 23:18">Bik 23:18</ref>; <ref loc="EPH 4:1">Bef 4:1</ref></char>
    </note>Nze Pawulo, Kristo Yesu yanfuula omusibe we, nsobole okuyamba mmwe Abaamawanga.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:2 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="COL 1:25">Bak 1:25</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Mwawulira ekisa kya Katonda kye naweebwa okubayamba. <verse number="3" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:3 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 16:25">Bar 16:25</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 2:10">1Ko 2:10</ref></char></note>Nga bwe nasooka okubawandiikira mu bimpimpi, Katonda alina okubikkulirwa okw’ekyama kwe yandaga. <verse number="4" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:4 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2CO 11:6">2Ko 11:6</ref></char></note>Bwe munaasoma ebbaluwa eno mujja kusobola okutegeera ebyo bye mmanyi ku kyama kya Kristo. <verse number="5" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:5 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 16:26">Bar 16:26</ref></char></note>Mu biro eby’edda, tewali yali amanyi kyama ekyo okutuusa Omwoyo wa Katonda bw’akibikkulidde abatume be abatukuvu ne bannabbi. <verse number="6" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:6 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GAL 3:29">Bag 3:29</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EPH 2:15">Bef 2:15</ref>, <ref loc="EPH 2:16">16</ref></char></note>Kino kye kyama kye njogerako: olw’enjiri ya Kristo, Abaamawanga balisikira wamu ne Isirayiri ekyo Katonda kye yasuubiza, era baliba omubiri gumu, era ne bagabanira wamu ekisuubizo ekyo mu Kristo Yesu.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:7 a </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1CO 3:5">1Ko 3:5</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">b </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EPH 1:19">Bef 1:19</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nafuuka omuweereza w’enjiri eyo olw’ekirabo eky’ekisa kya Katonda kye naweebwa, Katonda ng’akolera mu maanyi ge. <verse number="8" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:8 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 15:9">1Ko 15:9</ref></char></note>Newaakubadde nga nze nsembayo wansi mu batukuvu bonna, naweebwa ekisa ekyo, okubuulira Abaamawanga emikisa egiri mu Kristo egitageraageraganyizika. <verse number="9" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:9 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 16:25">Bar 16:25</ref></char></note>Katonda eyatonda ebintu byonna yayagala nnyambe buli muntu okutegeera ebyekyama ebyali bikwekeddwa mu Katonda. <verse number="10" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:10 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 2:7">1Ko 2:7</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1PE 1:12">1Pe 1:12</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">c </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EPH 1:21">Bef 1:21</ref></char></note>Katonda yakigenderera atyo, ng’ayita mu kkanisa, alyoke yeeyoleke eri amaanyi n’obuyinza ebiri mu nsi ey’omwoyo eya waggulu, ng’abalaga nga bw’alina amagezi amangi ag’ebika eby’enjawulo. <verse number="11" style="v"/>Katonda yakola bw’atyo ng’enteekateeka ye ey’emirembe n’emirembe bw’eri, gye yatuukiriza mu ebyo byonna Kristo Yesu Mukama waffe bye yakola. <verse number="12" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:12 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EPH 2:18">Bef 2:18</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="HEB 4:16">Beb 4:16</ref></char></note>Kristo atuwa obuvumu n’obugumu, tulyoke tusembere mu maaso ga Katonda olw’okukkiriza nga tetutya. <verse number="13" style="v"/>Kyenva mbeegayirira muleme kuterebuka olw’okubonaabona kwange ku lwammwe, kubanga ekyo kibaleetera kitiibwa.</para>
  <para style="s1">Okwagala kwa Kristo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:14 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PHP 2:10">Baf 2:10</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nfukaamirira Kitaffe, <verse number="15" style="v"/>ebika byonna eby’omu ggulu n’eby’oku nsi mwe biggya obulamu. <verse number="16" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:16 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="COL 1:11">Bak 1:11</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 7:22">Bar 7:22</ref></char></note>Nsaba Katonda oyo akola eby’ekitalo era agulumizibwa, agumyenga era anywezenga omuntu wammwe ow’omunda, olw’Omwoyo we, <verse number="17" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:17 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 14:23">Yk 14:23</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="COL 1:23">Bak 1:23</ref></char></note>Kristo alyoke abeerenga mu mitima gyammwe olw’okukkiriza kwammwe. Mbasabira mubeerenga n’emirandira mu kwagala nga mukunywereddemu, <verse number="18" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:18 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JOB 11:8">Yob 11:8</ref>, <ref loc="JOB 11:9">9</ref></char></note>mulyoke mubeerenga n’amaanyi awamu n’abatukuvu bonna, okusobola okutegeera obugazi, n’obuwanvu, n’obugulumivu n’okukka wansi ebiri mu kwagala kwa Kristo. <verse number="19" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:19 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="COL 2:10">Bak 2:10</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EPH 1:23">Bef 1:23</ref></char></note>Njagala mutegeere okwagala kwa Kristo okusukkiridde okutegeera kwonna, mulyoke musobole okutegeerera ddala Katonda bw’ali.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:20 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 16:25">Bar 16:25</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Kaakano nsaba nti oyo akola ebintu byonna okusinga byonna bye tusaba, ne bye tulowooza, ng’amaanyi ge bwe gali agakolera mu ffe, <verse number="21" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:21 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 11:36">Bar 11:36</ref></char></note>agulumizibwenga mu Kkanisa ne mu Kristo Yesu, emirembe n’emirembe. Amiina.</para>
  <chapter number="4" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Okuba ab’omubiri ogumu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:1 a </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EPH 3:1">Bef 3:1</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">b </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PHP 1:27">Baf 1:27</ref>; <ref loc="COL 1:10">Bak 1:10</ref></char>
    </note>Ng’omusibe wa Mukama waffe, mbakuutira mubeere n’empisa ezisaanira obulamu bwe mwayitirwa okutambuliramu. <verse number="2" style="v"/>Mubeerenga bakkakkamu, abawombeefu era abagumiikiriza, nga mugumiikirizagana mu kwagala. <verse number="3" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:3 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="COL 3:14">Bak 3:14</ref></char></note>Munyiikirenga okukuuma obumu obw’Omwoyo mu kwegatta awamu okw’emirembe. <verse number="4" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:4 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 12:13">1Ko 12:13</ref></char></note>Omubiri nga bwe guli ogumu, n’Omwoyo omu, n’essuubi liri limu ery’okuyitibwa kwammwe. <verse number="5" style="v"/>Mukama waffe ali omu, n’okukkiriza kumu n’okubatizibwa kumu. <verse number="6" style="v"/>Katonda ali omu, era ye Kitaawe wa bonna, afuga byonna, akolera mu byonna era abeera mu byonna.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:7 a </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1CO 12:7">1Ko 12:7</ref>, <ref loc="1CO 12:11">11</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">b </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 12:3">Bar 12:3</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Buli omu ku ffe yaweebwa ekisa ng’okugera kwa Kristo bwe kuli. <verse number="8" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:8 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="COL 2:15">Bak 2:15</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PSA 68:18">Zab 68:18</ref></char></note>Ebyawandiikibwa kyebiva bigamba nti,</para>
  <para style="q1">“Bwe yalinnya mu ggulu,</para>
  <para style="q2">n’atwala omunyago,</para>
  <para style="q2">n’awa abantu ebirabo.”</para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>Okugamba nti “yalinnya,” kitegeeza ki? Kitegeeza nti yasooka kukka mu bitundu ebya wansi w’ensi. <verse number="10" style="v"/>Oyo Kristo eyakka, ye wuuyo ddala eyalinnya ewala ennyo, n’ayisa waggulu w’eggulu lyonna, alyoke ajjule obwengula bw’ensi yonna. <verse number="11" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:11 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 12:28">1Ko 12:28</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 21:8">Bik 21:8</ref></char></note>Era y’omu oyo eyawa abamu okuba abatume, n’abalala okuba bannabbi, n’abalala okuba ababuulizi b’enjiri, n’abalala okuba abasumba, n’abalala okuba abayigiriza. <verse number="12" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:12 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 12:27">1Ko 12:27</ref></char></note>Ekyo yakikola olw’okutendeka abantu ba Katonda olw’omulimu ogw’obuweereza, okuzimba omubiri gwa Kristo. <verse number="13" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:13 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false">nny 3, 5 </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="COL 1:28">Bak 1:28</ref></char></note>Ekyo kijja kutwongera okugenda mu maaso, okutuusa ffenna lwe tulibeera n’okukkiriza kumu, n’okumanyira ddala Omwana wa Katonda nga tukulidde ddala mu mwoyo okutuuka ku kigera eky’okubeera nga Kristo bw’ali.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:14 a </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1CO 14:20">1Ko 14:20</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">b </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JAS 1:6">Yak 1:6</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">c </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EPH 6:11">Bef 6:11</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Tuteekwa okulekeraawo okweyisa ng’abaana abato, nga tuyuuguumizibwa amayengo nga tutwalibwa buli muyaga ogw’okuyigiriza okw’abantu abakuusa, mu nkwe olw’okugoberera enteekateeka ey’obulimba. <verse number="15" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:15 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EPH 1:22">Bef 1:22</ref></char></note>Tube ba mazima mu kwagala, tulyoke tukulire mu Kristo mu byonna, nga tweyongera okuba nga ye, Omutwe gw’Ekkanisa. <verse number="16" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:16 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="COL 2:19">Bak 2:19</ref></char></note>Mu ye omubiri gwonna mwe gugattirwa obulungi awamu, ne guyungibwa mu buli nnyingo, nga gukola ng’ekigera kya buli kitundu bwe kuli, nga gukula era nga gwezimba mu kwagala.</para>
  <para style="s1">Obulamu obuggya mu Kristo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:17 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 1:21">Bar 1:21</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Ng’omugoberezi wa Mukama waffe, mbalagira okulekeraawo okutambula ng’abatamanyi Katonda bwe batambulira mu birowoozo byabwe eby’obusirusiru. <verse number="18" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:18 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 1:21">Bar 1:21</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EPH 2:12">Bef 2:12</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">c </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2CO 3:14">2Ko 3:14</ref></char></note>Amagezi gaabwe gajjudde ekizikiza. Tebalina mugabo mu by’obulamu bwa Katonda, kubanga bajjudde obutamanya era emitima gyabwe mikakanyavu. <verse number="19" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:19 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TI 4:2">1Ti 4:2</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 1:24">Bar 1:24</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">c </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="COL 3:5">Bak 3:5</ref></char></note>Tebakyalina nsonyi, beemalidde mu bya buwemu, na mululu gwa kukola bya bugwenyufu ebya buli ngeri.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>Kyokka mmwe si bwe mwayigirizibwa ku bya Kristo. <verse number="21" style="v"/>Obanga ddala mwamuwulira, era ne muyigirizibwa mu ye ng’amazima bwe gali mu Yesu, <verse number="22" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:22 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1PE 2:1">1Pe 2:1</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 6:6">Bar 6:6</ref></char></note>kale mwambulemu obulamu obw’omuntu ow’edda, avunda olw’okwegomba okw’obulimba. <verse number="23" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:23 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="COL 3:10">Bak 3:10</ref></char></note>Mufuuke baggya olw’Omwoyo afuga ebirowoozo byammwe, <verse number="24" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:24 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 6:4">Bar 6:4</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EPH 2:10">Bef 2:10</ref></char></note>era mwambale omuntu omuggya, eyatondebwa mu kifaananyi kya Katonda mu butuukirivu ne mu kutukuzibwa okw’amazima.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:25 a </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ZEC 8:16">Zek 8:16</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">b </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 12:5">Bar 12:5</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Mulekeraawo okulimba, mwogerenga amazima buli muntu ne munne, kubanga tuli bitundu bya mubiri gumu. <verse number="26" style="v"/>“Bwe musunguwalanga mwekuume muleme kwonoona.” Temuzibyanga budde nga mukyasunguwadde. <verse number="27" style="v"/>Temuwanga Setaani bbanga. <verse number="28" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:28 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 20:35">Bik 20:35</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TH 4:11">1Bs 4:11</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">c </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 3:11">Luk 3:11</ref></char></note>Abadde omubbi alekeraawo okubba, wabula anyiikirenga okukola eby’omugaso ng’akola n’emikono gye, alyoke afune ky’agabirako n’abo abeetaaga.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v"/>Mwekuume mulemenga okwogera ebigambo ebitasaana, wabula mwogerenga ebyo byokka ebizimba nga buli muntu bwe yeetaaga, biryoke bigase abo ababiwulira. <verse number="30" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:30 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TH 5:19">1Bs 5:19</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 8:23">Bar 8:23</ref></char></note>Era temunakuwazanga Mwoyo Mutukuvu wa Katonda, eyabateekako akabonero akalaga nga mwanunulibwa. <verse number="31" style="v"/>Okunyiiga, n’obusungu, n’obukambwe, n’okukaayana, n’okuvuma, na buli kibi kyonna, biremenga kubeera mu mmwe. <verse number="32" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:32 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 6:14">Mat 6:14</ref>, <ref loc="MAT 6:15">15</ref></char></note>Mubenga ba kisa, buli omu alumirwenga munne, era musonyiwaganenga, nga Katonda bwe yabasonyiwa mu Kristo.</para>
  <chapter number="5" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Okubeera mu Musana</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>Mufubenga okufaanana Katonda kubanga muli baana ba Katonda abaagalwa. <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:2 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GAL 1:4">Bag 1:4</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2CO 2:15">2Ko 2:15</ref></char></note>Mwagalanenga nga Kristo bwe yatwagala ne yeewaayo ku lwaffe n’afuuka ekiweebwayo era ssaddaaka eri Katonda, eyakawoowo akalungi.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">5:3 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="COL 3:5">Bak 3:5</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nga bwe muli abantu ba Katonda abatukuvu, obwenzi, n’obugwagwa bwonna, n’omululu bireme okuwulirwa mu mmwe. <verse number="4" style="v"/>Mwewale okwogera eby’ensonyi, n’eby’obusirusiru, n’okubalaata ebitasaana. Mwebazenga bwebaza Katonda. <verse number="5" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:5 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="COL 3:5">Bak 3:5</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 6:9">1Ko 6:9</ref></char></note>Mukimanye era mukitegeerere ddala nga buli mwenzi, oba omugwagwa, oba eyeegomba, aba asinza bakatonda abalala, talina mugabo mu bwakabaka bwa Kristo ne Katonda. <verse number="6" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:6 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 1:18">Bar 1:18</ref></char></note>Omuntu yenna tabalimbalimbanga n’ebigambo ebitaliimu. Katonda abonereza buli muntu yenna amujeemera. <verse number="7" style="v"/>Noolwekyo temwegattanga n’abafaanana ng’abo.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">5:8 a </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EPH 2:2">Bef 2:2</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">b </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LUK 16:8">Luk 16:8</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Edda mwali ng’abantu ab’ekizikiza, naye kaakano muli bantu ba musana mu Mukama waffe. Noolwekyo mutambulenga ng’abaana ab’omusana, <verse number="9" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:9 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GAL 5:22">Bag 5:22</ref></char></note>ekitangaala kyammwe kirabisibwe. Mubale ebibala eby’omusana nga mweyisa bulungi, nga mubeera abeesimbu era ab’amazima, <verse number="10" style="v"/>nga munoonya ekyo ekisanyusa Mukama waffe. <verse number="11" style="v"/>Temwenyigiranga mu bikolwa bya kizikiza kubanga tebigasa, wabula munenyenga ababikola. <verse number="12" style="v"/>Kubanga kya nsonyi n’okubyogerako ebyo abajeemu bye bakolera mu kyama. <verse number="13" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:13 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 3:20">Yk 3:20</ref>, <ref loc="JHN 3:21">21</ref></char></note>Byonna bwe biryatuukirizibwa mu kitangaala, birirabikira ddala nga bwe biri. <verse number="14" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:14 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 13:11">Bar 13:11</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 5:25">Yk 5:25</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">c </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ISA 60:1">Is 60:1</ref></char></note>Ekitangaala kirabisa buli kintu. Kyekiva kigambibwa nti,</para>
  <para style="q1">“Zuukuka ggwe eyeebase,</para>
  <para style="q2">Ozuukire mu bafu,</para>
  <para style="q2">Kristo anaakwakira.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>Mutunule nga mutambula n’obwegendereza, si ng’abatalina magezi wabula ng’abalina amagezi, <verse number="16" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:16 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="COL 4:5">Bak 4:5</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EPH 6:13">Bef 6:13</ref></char></note>nga temwonoona biseera kubanga ennaku zino mbi. <verse number="17" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:17 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 12:2">Bar 12:2</ref>; <ref loc="1TH 4:3">1Bs 4:3</ref></char></note>Temubanga basirusiru, naye mutegeere Mukama waffe ky’ayagala. <verse number="18" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:18 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PRO 20:1">Nge 20:1</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 1:15">Luk 1:15</ref></char></note>Ate temutamiiranga, kubanga mujja kweyonoona, wabula Omwoyo ajjulenga mu bulamu bwammwe. <verse number="19" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:19 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 16:25">Bik 16:25</ref>; <ref loc="COL 3:16">Bak 3:16</ref></char></note>Bwe mukuŋŋananga muzimbaganenga mu Zabbuli ne mu nnyimba, ne mu nnyimba ez’Omwoyo nga muyimbira Mukama era nga mumuyimusiza amaloboozi mu mutima gwammwe. <verse number="20" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:20 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PSA 34:1">Zab 34:1</ref></char></note>Bulijjo mwebazenga Katonda Kitaffe olwa byonna, mu linnya lya Mukama waffe Yesu Kristo.</para>
  <para style="s1">Abakazi ne ba bbaabwe</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">5:21 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GAL 5:13">Bag 5:13</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Mutyenga Kristo, nga muwuliragananga.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">5:22 a </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 3:16">Lub 3:16</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">b </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EPH 6:5">Bef 6:5</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Abakazi, muwulirenga babbammwe nga bwe muwulira Mukama waffe. <verse number="23" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:23 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 11:3">1Ko 11:3</ref>; <ref loc="EPH 1:22">Bef 1:22</ref></char></note>Omusajja gwe mutwe gw’omukazi, nga Kristo bw’ali omutwe gw’Ekkanisa. Ekkanisa gwe mubiri gwa Kristo, era ye yennyini ye Mulokozi waagwo. <verse number="24" style="v"/>Kale ng’Ekkanisa bw’ewulira Kristo, n’abakazi bwe batyo bwe basaana okuwuliranga ba bbaabwe mu byonna.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">5:25 a </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="COL 3:19">Bak 3:19</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">b </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">nny 2</char>
    </note>Nammwe abaami mwagalenga bakyala bammwe nga Kristo bwe yayagala Ekkanisa ne yeewaayo ku lwayo. <verse number="26" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:26 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 22:16">Bik 22:16</ref></char></note>Yaginaaza n’amazzi, n’agitukuza n’ekigambo kye, <verse number="27" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:27 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EPH 1:4">Bef 1:4</ref>; <ref loc="COL 1:22">Bak 1:22</ref></char></note>alyoke yeefunire Ekkanisa ey’ekitiibwa, eteriiko bbala wadde akamogo oba ekintu kyonna ekikyamu, wabula ebeere entukuvu, etuukiridde. <verse number="28" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:28 </char><char style="xt" closed="false">nny 25</char></note>N’abasajja bwe batyo bwe basaana okwagalanga bakazi baabwe, nga bwe baagala emibiri gyabwe gyennyini. Ayagala mukazi we yeeyagala yekka. <verse number="29" style="v"/>Tewali n’omu yali akyaye omubiri gwe, wabula aguliisa era agujjanjaba nga Kristo bw’ajjanjaba Ekkanisa ye, <verse number="30" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:30 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 12:27">1Ko 12:27</ref></char></note>kubanga tuli bitundu bya mubiri gwe. <verse number="31" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:31 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GEN 2:24">Lub 2:24</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 19:5">Mat 19:5</ref>; <ref loc="1CO 6:16">1Ko 6:16</ref></char></note>“Kale omusajja kyanaavanga aleka kitaawe ne nnyina ne yeegatta ne mukazi we, ne bafuuka omuntu omu.” <verse number="32" style="v"/>Ekyama kino kikulu, kyokka nze ndowooza nti kyogera ku Kristo n’Ekkanisa ye. <verse number="33" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:33 </char><char style="xt" closed="false">nny 25</char></note>Kale, nammwe buli musajja ayagalenga mukazi we nga bwe yeeyagala yennyini, era n’omukazi assengamu bba ekitiibwa.</para>
  <chapter number="6" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Abazadde n’abaana baabwe</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">6:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="COL 3:20">Bak 3:20</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Abaana, muwulirenga bazadde bammwe mu Mukama waffe, kubanga bwe mukola mutyo, mukola kituufu. <verse number="2" style="v"/>“Kitaawo ne nnyoko obassangamu ekitiibwa,” eryo lye tteeka erisooka eririmu okusuubiza nti: <verse number="3" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:3 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EXO 20:12">Kuv 20:12</ref></char></note>Bw’onoobanga obulungi, era n’owangaala ku nsi. <verse number="4" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:4 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="COL 3:21">Bak 3:21</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GEN 18:19">Lub 18:19</ref>; <ref loc="DEU 6:7">Ma 6:7</ref></char></note>Nammwe abazadde, temunyigirizanga baana bammwe, wabula mubakuze nga mubagunjula era nga mubayigiriza ebya Mukama waffe.</para>
  <para style="s1">Abaddu ne bakama baabwe</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">6:5 a </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1TI 6:1">1Ti 6:1</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">b </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="COL 3:22">Bak 3:22</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">c </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EPH 5:22">Bef 5:22</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Abaddu, muwulirenga bakama bammwe ab’omu mubiri nga mubatya era nga mubawa ekitiibwa ng’omutima gwammwe mumalirivu, nga bwe mwamalirira mu Kristo. <verse number="6" style="v"/>Ekyo temukikola lwa kulabibwa, abantu balyoke babasiime, wabula mukolenga ng’abaddu ba Kristo nga mukola n’omutima gwammwe gwonna, nga Katonda bw’ayagala. <verse number="7" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:7 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="COL 3:23">Bak 3:23</ref></char></note>Muweerezenga n’omutima omulungi ng’abakolera Mukama waffe so si ng’abakolera abantu, <verse number="8" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:8 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="COL 3:24">Bak 3:24</ref></char></note>nga mumanyi ng’ekirungi kyonna omuntu ky’akola, oba muddu oba wa ddembe, Mukama alimusasula empeera ennungi. <verse number="9" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:9 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JOB 31:13">Yob 31:13</ref>, <ref loc="JOB 31:14">14</ref></char></note>Era nammwe bakama b’abaddu, muyisenga bulungi abaddu bammwe nga temubatiisatiisa, nga mumanyi nti Mukama waabwe, ye Mukama wammwe, ali mu ggulu era ye tasosola mu bantu.</para>
  <para style="s1">Ebyokulwanyisa bya Katonda</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">6:10 a </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1CO 16:13">1Ko 16:13</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">b </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EPH 1:19">Bef 1:19</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Eky’enkomerero, mubenga n’amaanyi mu Mukama waffe ne mu buyinza obw’amaanyi ge. <verse number="11" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:11 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 13:12">Bar 13:12</ref></char></note>Mwambale ebyokulwanyisa byonna ebya Katonda, mulyoke musobole okwolekera enkwe za Setaani. <verse number="12" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:12 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EPH 1:21">Bef 1:21</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 8:38">Bar 8:38</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">c </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EPH 1:3">Bef 1:3</ref></char></note>Kubanga tetumeggana na mubiri wadde musaayi, wabula tulwanyisa abafuzi, n’ab’obuyinza, n’amaanyi ag’ensi ag’ekizikiza, n’emyoyo emibi egy’omu bifo ebya waggulu. <verse number="13" style="v"/>Noolwekyo mwambalenga ebyokulwanyisa byonna ebya Katonda, mulyoke musobole okwaŋŋanga omulabe ku lunaku olw’akabi, era bwe mulimala okukola byonna, mulyoke musigale nga muli banywevu. <verse number="14" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:14 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ISA 11:5">Is 11:5</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ISA 59:17">Is 59:17</ref></char></note>Muyimirire nga muli banywevu, ng’amazima lwe lukoba lwammwe lwe mwesibye mu kiwato kyammwe, ate ng’obutuukirivu kye ky’omu kifuba, <verse number="15" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:15 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ISA 52:7">Is 52:7</ref></char></note>nga mwambadde n’engatto mu bigere byammwe nga mugenda okubuulira Enjiri ey’emirembe. <verse number="16" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:16 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1JN 5:4">1Yk 5:4</ref></char></note>Era ku ebyo byonna okukkiriza kwammwe kubeerenga engabo eneebasobozesanga okuzikiza obusaale bwonna obw’omuliro obulasibwa omubi. <verse number="17" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:17 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ISA 59:17">Is 59:17</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="HEB 4:12">Beb 4:12</ref></char></note>Obulokozi bubafuukire enkuufiira gye mwambadde, n’ekigambo kya Katonda kibabeerere ekitala eky’Omwoyo, <verse number="18" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:18 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 18:1">Luk 18:1</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 26:41">Mat 26:41</ref>; <ref loc="PHP 1:4">Baf 1:4</ref></char></note>nga musabiririranga mu ssaala zonna nga mwegayiririranga mu mwoyo buli kiseera. Mwekuumenga nga mugumiikirizanga, era nga mwegayiririranga abatukuvu, be bantu bonna aba Katonda.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">6:19 a </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1TH 5:25">1Bs 5:25</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">b </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ACT 4:29">Bik 4:29</ref>; <ref loc="2CO 3:12">2Ko 3:12</ref></char>
    </note>Era nange munsabirenga bwe nnaabanga njogera mpeebwe eby’okwogera, era mbyogerenga n’obuvumu nga ntegeeza abantu ekyama ky’Enjiri. <verse number="20" style="v"/>Ndi mubaka wa Njiri ali mu njegere. Munsabire ndyoke ngibuulire abantu n’obuvumu nga bwe kinsaanira.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">6:21 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ACT 20:4">Bik 20:4</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Tukiko, owooluganda omwagalwa era omuweereza omwesigwa mu Mukama waffe, alibategeeza byonna mulyoke mutegeere ebinfaako ne bye nkola. <verse number="22" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:22 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="COL 4:7-9">Bak 4:7-9</ref></char></note>Mmutumye gye muli, mulyoke mumanye nga bwe tuli era abagumye emitima gyammwe.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">6:23 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GAL 6:16">Bag 6:16</ref>; <ref loc="1PE 5:14">1Pe 5:14</ref></char>
    </note>Emirembe n’okwagala awamu n’okukkiriza ebiva eri Katonda Kitaffe ne Mukama waffe Yesu Kristo, bibeerenga n’abooluganda.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v"/>Ekisa kya Katonda kibeerenga n’abo bonna abaagala Mukama waffe Yesu Kristo n’okwagala okutaggwaawo.</para>
</usx>
